description:
By Waqas

In a major blow to cybercrime, Breach Forums, a notorious online marketplace for stolen data, has been seized by the FBI and Department of Justice (DoJ). This unprecedented takedown includes not just the clear web domain, but also the dark web, escrow sections and Telegram accounts.

This is a post from HackRead.com Read the original post: Popular Cyber Crime Forum Breach Forums Seized by Police
title: Popular Cyber Crime Forum Breach Forums Seized by Police

By Deeba Ahmed

Is FIDO2 truly unbreachable?  Recent research exposes a potential vulnerability where attackers could use MITM techniques to bypass FIDO2 security keys.

This is a post from HackRead.com Read the original post: MITM Attacks Can Still Bypass FIDO2 Security, Researchers Warn
title: MITM Attacks Can Still Bypass FIDO2 Security, Researchers Warn
